00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:36,800
Now, value investing just means investing in stocks

487
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:39,000
that are trading below their perceived intrinsic value.

488
00:15:39,260 --> 00:15:41,120
So if you kind of want to make

489
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:43,340
a very simple analogy, value investing is kind

490
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:45,060
