00:15:45,060 --> 00:15:47,040
75 cents and hoping that you can sell

492
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:48,340
it again for a dollar later.

493
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:51,020
So value investing is a very popular investing

494
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:52,880
strategy because many of the world's best historical

495
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:55,340
investors like Warren Buffett, Seth Clareman, and Benjamin

496
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:57,500
